title: Kiddie Porn - A Gift of Hate
description:
Kiddie Porn was a side project of Godsmack current drummer Shannon Larkin when he was in a band called Wrathchild back in 1986.

This is a 320Kbps RIP direct from the cassette tape Shannon gave to our drummer and he to me.
